Source-Makefile: feeds/packages/libs/openldap/Makefile
Package: libopenldap
Version: 2.4.19-2
Depends: +libopenssl +libsasl2
Provides: 
Build-Depends: libtool
Section: libs
Category: Libraries
Title: LDAP implementation (libraries)
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: openldap-2.4.19.tgz
Type: ipkg
Description: 	OpenLDAP Software is an open source implementation of the 
	Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP).	
	This package contains the shared LDAP client libraries, needed by other programs.
http://www.openldap.org/
@@

